<h3><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Child Support / Maintenance</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Child Support and maintenance is an income that is received to assist with the care of dependent children.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">There is no need to use child support/maintenance income when servicing can be satisfactorily demonstrated from the customer's income.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">For information on child support payments refer to Child Support Agency website.</span></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
